Furthermore, adding ReplyFormat class to format the reply Duke reply to the user.

Procedure of Duke:
1) Greet the user
2) Waiting for user input
3) Reply what user input back to user
4) If bye encounter, exit program. Else, repeat steps 2 and 3.
